ge parking area adjacent to the braun music center dinkelspiel auditorium and tressider memorial union from el camino real exit el camino real at university avenue turn toward the hills away from the center of palo alto as you enter stanford university avenue becomes palm drive go through one traffic light and turn left onto campus drive east at the first stop sign continue on campus drive east until you reach mayfield avenue and make a right after the next stop sign take the first right into a large parking area adjacent to braun music center dinkelspiel auditorium and tressider memorial union parking near braun music center the tressider lot has coin metered spaces at $1.50 hour and pay and display spaces a self serve machine in the tressider lot issues one day visitor permits for $12.00 good for up to 8 hours display the receipt on your dashboard and park in either the pay and display or metered spaces the permit dispenser accepts credit cards cash or coins it does not issue change please note that parking is monitored monday friday 8am 4pm for more information see parking & transportation services back stanford university stanford california 94305 650 725 1064 terms of use copyright complaints
